---
title: Easy Caribbean Pulled Chicken & Coconut Sauce with Charred Pineapple Salsa & Carrot Slaw
description: Eat the tropical rainbow tonight with this vibrant collection of veggies and pulled chicken cooked in our mild Caribbean jerk
seasoning. We’re keeping those beach vibes going by adding sweet and juicy charred pineapple slices and a hint of nutty
peanuts.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

